I’m not allergic to animals, just dog saliva so drooling dogs are a no go for me. I actually owned a cat and was never allergic but AFTER being around dog saliva (thinking maybe it was only one dog) it caused me to start getting sniffly from my baby too. I started making sure I kept him from shedding as much, that’s all.

snippet.textDisplay:
Sometimes I forget that jack isn't just a good friend of mine.


earlier today I was wondering how I was gonna tell him that he pretty much saved me from myself, and only now I remember that I won't ever be able to tell him. He probably won't see this, but I still want him to know that he is,


ABSOLUTELY AMAZING.


How on earth do you make someone forget that you don't actually know them?


And more importantly


How on earth do you save someone from their own mind when you don't even know their name? or anything about them?


Just a reminder; you are doing great, and you saved so many people from spiralling into a dark place/got them out of it. I cannot stress this enough, YOU ARE SO FUCKING AMAZING.


-Aoki
